# Frontend environment variables (Vite). Copy to ".env" only if you need to
# override the API URL.
#
# Local development: leave VITE_API_URL UNSET — Vite proxies /api to the backend
# on :5000 (see vite.config.ts).
#
# Production (e.g. Vercel): set VITE_API_URL to your deployed backend URL,
# INCLUDING the /api path. Example:
#
#   VITE_API_URL=https://your-api.up.railway.app/api
